okbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-III-look-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-III-look.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eabove Hot Escape Cheek Palette III + Afterglow Lip Oil in Laguna\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSwatches of all three palettes below:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Summer 2025 Hot Escape Collection Review Cheek Palettes swatches\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025. A look at the new Hot Escape Cheek Palettes, Lip Oils and new Eyeshadow Sticks.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/04/nars-hot-escape-summer-2025.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Cheek-Palette-Swatches.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e____________\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eTotal Seduction Eyeshadow Stick\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Total Seduction Eyeshadow Stick\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025. A look at the new Hot Escape Cheek Palettes, Lip Oils and new Eyeshadow Sticks.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/04/nars-hot-escape-summer-2025.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-Total-Seduction-Eyeshadows.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shades of the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/42OkqCF\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eTotal Seduction Cream Eyeshadow Stick\u003c/a\u003e ($32 each) this season are so beautiful. I think they apply beautifully to the lids and I really love the tones. Once they are applied they do not budge so blend quickly once you put these on the lids. Ablaze is a beautiful champagne sparkle, Hustle is the prettiest copper gold shimmer and Sparked is a warm auburn shimmer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Total Seduction Eyeshadow Stick swatches\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025. A look at the new Hot Escape Cheek Palettes, Lip Oils and new Eyeshadow Sticks.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/04/nars-hot-escape-summer-2025.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Hot-Escape-Summer-Eyeshadow-Sticks-swatches.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs beautiful as they are I think they are very similar to shades from Laura Mercier or Bobbi Brown so I don’t think they are must-haves. I am thrilled that they decided to keep the Laguna Eyeshadow Quad (reviewed and swatched here) which is one of the best neutrals I’ve tried. It looks like it’s now permanent. I think it’s a must-have.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eHot Escape Afterglow Lip Oil\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Hot Escape Afterglow Lip Oils\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025. A look at the new Hot Escape Cheek Palettes, Lip Oils and new Eyeshadow Sticks.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/04/nars-hot-escape-summer-2025.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Summer-2025-High-Life-Lip-Oils.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLast a quick look at the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4cyS8PU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eHot Escape Afterglow Lip Oils\u003c/a\u003e ($28 each). These are very thin in texture but smooth without any sticky feel. They are also very sheer for a barely there look. Formula wise I give them a 10/10 rating. I would have definitely loved to see more pigment as the colors are really pretty but are so sheer they barely show up on the lips. Laguna has the best pigment while the others are almost transparent.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHigh Life\u003c/span\u003e is a sheer pink\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrgasm\u003c/span\u003e is a shimmery pink gold\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLaguna\u003c/span\u003e is a shimmery bronze\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWonderous\u003c/span\u003e is a sheer purple berry\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"NARS Hot Escape Afterglow Lip Oils\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025. A look at the new Hot Escape Cheek Palettes, Lip Oils and new Eyeshadow Sticks.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/04/nars-hot-escape-summer-2025.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"NARS Hot Escape Summer 2025\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NARS-Afterglow-Lip-Oil-swatches.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThey do layer beautifully over a liner or lipstick! And I know a lot of you want just a subtle hint of color for spring or summer vacations. I love the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/42CZf5t\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eHigh Life Lip Oil\u003c/a\u003e layered on top of the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4iEO16x\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eHermes Shine Lipstick\u003c/a\u003e in Rose Himalaya (also in action \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DIjw5gOJt0K/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cem\u003ehere\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI do think for a more pigmented lip oil option the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3WICtGn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eHermes Hermesistible Lip Oils\u003c/a\u003e are the best even though they are incredibly expensive. Formula and colors \u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2022/04/hermesistible-infused-lip-care-oil-review.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ereviewed here\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e and they’re all summer perfection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOverall lots to love. The Cheek Palettes are the stand outs to me. I love that they have everything you need for a complete cheek look and I like using the bronzer and highlighter shades on the eyes too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou can find the collection out now. Available at \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3YBtJmS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eNordstrom\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3E8Z8WW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eSephora\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/44ADDsP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eUlta Beauty\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/42Eigo0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eBloomingdale’s\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/42LBYhN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eNARS Cosmetics\u003c/a\u003e along with all other NARS retailers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eHot Escape Palette III, Lip Oil in Orgasm and Laguna and the Total Seduction Eyeshadows gifted. All others purchased by me.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
